name: Colorful Stuffed Dumpling #009
description: The colorful stuffed dumpling is filled with pork, bamboo shoots, shrimp, ginger and chives. This dumpling is very well-seasoned and full of flavor! The shape is unique and folded in a way that leaves 4 quadrant openings at the top which are filled with , egg white, egg yolk, carrot and chives to give it an esthetic appearance. The colorful stuffed dumpling is served hot and fresh!
